sections.heading: of lien; disposition of deposit
sections.text: If such judgment be affirmed, the money so deposited shall be paid to the judgment creditor, but if such judgment be reversed, the debtor may withdraw such deposit.SourceLaws 1893, c. 42, § 2, p. 384;R.S.1913, § 8000;C.S.1922, § 8941;C.S.1929, § 20-1307;R.S.1943, § 25
